notes.note:
Mike at Terrace Ford called. Needs A/C condenser. He quoted well over $400.00. I suggested he contact Auto Climate. He immediately complained that he wanted to use a Ford part and the customer likely does too. I asked why since it was a Ford part that failed in the first place. I gave him Auto Climate's number and told him we would offer a 30% mark up if he ordered it. I asked for an email quote which he whined about as well. "Other third party warranties take quotes over the phone". He kept complaining that this was a hassle. I suggested that, if this was too much trouble for him,  I could have another shop do this claim without the complaints and push back. He will send a quote.
BTW, he admitted the Ford part was back ordered for weeks. A.H.
